summary: Apart from a passion for helping people discover music and music videos, what's made me tick throughout my career is working with a team of likeminded, creative people who are truly passionate about their work. I also love having the opportunity to be a part of global product launches, and getting the chance to work with people from all over the world. I've managed geographically dispersed teams quite a bit, and there is always a lot to learn from this.
